


Setup
-----

Obtain specific version of iverilog.

    Clone: https://github.com/steveicarus/iverilog

    Checkout one of the revisions known to work. Previous or later versions may have bugs or missing features.

    Latest : commit bd0a1c75edc2644ec093c8e6940a4d0f6373f4b2
    Earlier: commit 9d15b771b15141c7f394cf7f2e5f935da47f6534 


Build iverilog and install iverilog - see the iverilog docs.



Running main cpu simulation
-----

cd cpu/
../simulate.sh


